                "readme": "# appl_1\n\nFull-stack CRUD app — React TypeScript frontend, Spring Boot backend, MySQL.\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- **Frontend**: React 17 + TypeScript + Bootstrap — `client/`\n- **Backend**: Spring Boot 3.1 + Spring Data JPA — `server/`\n- **Database**: MySQL\n\n## Running\n\n```bash\ncd server && mvn spring-boot:run   # Spring Boot API on port 8080\ncd client && npm start             # React app\n```\n",
                "aboutTxt": null,
                "commentsTxt": null,
                "buildFiles": [],
