            "readme": "# accessing-data-mysql\n\nOfficial Spring guide — accessing data with MySQL.\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- Spring Boot 4.0\n- Spring Data JPA\n- MySQL (+ Docker Compose integration)\n- Testcontainers (testing)\n- Java 21 / Maven\n\n## Running\n\n```bash\nmvn spring-boot:run\n```\n\nRequires MySQL or Docker.\n",
            "aboutTxt": "use docker\r\n\r\nusername : root\r\npassword : verysecret\r\n\r\nrun script CREATE TABLE `mydatabase`.`user` ...\r\n\r\n\r\n./mvnw spring-boot:run\r\n\r\nhttp://localhost:8080/demo/all\r\n[{\"email\":\"name1@qmail.com\",\"id\":1,\"name\":\"name 1\"}]\r\n\r\nhttp://localhost:8080/demo/user/1\r\n{\"email\":\"name1@qmail.com\",\"id\":1,\"name\":\"name 1\"}\r\n\r\nhttp://localhost:8080/demo/user/2\r\ncom.example.accessing_data_mysql.UserNotFoundException: User 2 not found\r\n\r\nhttp://localhost:8080/demo/usersbyemail/name1@qmail.com\r\n{\"email\":\"name1@qmail.com\",\"id\":1,\"name\":\"name 1\"}\r\n\r\nsee comments in AccessingDataMysqlApplication",
