            "readme": "# accessing-data-rest\n\nOfficial Spring guide — exposing JPA repositories as REST endpoints via Spring Data REST.\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- Spring Boot 4.0\n- Spring Data JPA + Spring Data REST\n- H2 (in-memory)\n- Java 21 / Maven\n\n## Description\n\nJPA repositories are automatically exposed as HATEOAS REST endpoints — no controller code required.\n\n## Running\n\n```bash\nmvn spring-boot:run\n```\n",
