            "readme": "# SpringBootWithH2Database\n\nSpring Boot with H2 in-memory database and JPA.\n\n## Tech Stack\n\n- Spring Boot 4.0\n- Spring Data JPA\n- H2 (in-memory)\n- Lombok\n- Java 25 / Maven\n\n## Running\n\n```bash\nmvn spring-boot:run\n```\n\nH2 console at `/h2-console`. No external database needed.\n",
            "aboutTxt": "http://localhost:8082/h2-console\r\n\r\nSELECT * FROM DEPARTMENT ORDER BY DEPARTMENT_ID;\r\nINSERT INTO DEPARTMENT VALUES(1, 'address', 'code', 'name');\r\n\r\nhttp://localhost:8082/departments\r\n[{\"departmentId\":1,\"departmentName\":\"name\",\"departmentAddress\":\"address\",\"departmentCode\":\"code\"}]\r\n\r\nhttp://localhost:8082/departments/1\r\n{\"departmentId\":1,\"departmentName\":\"name\",\"departmentAddress\":\"address\",\"departmentCode\":\"code\"}\r\n",
