                "content": "name: expense_tracker2\ndescription: A personal expense tracker built with Flutter.\npublish_to: 'none'\n\nversion: 1.0.0+1\n\nenvironment:\n  sdk: '>=3.3.0 <4.0.0'\n\ndependencies:\n  flutter:\n    sdk: flutter\n\n  # State management\n  flutter_riverpod: ^2.5.1\n  hooks_riverpod: ^2.5.1\n  flutter_hooks: ^0.20.5\n  riverpod_annotation: ^2.3.5\n\n  # Navigation\n  go_router: ^14.2.7\n\n  # HTTP\n  dio: ^5.4.3+1\n\n  # Code generation - models\n  freezed_annotation: ^2.4.1\n  json_annotation: ^4.9.0\n\n  # Charts\n  fl_chart: ^0.68.0\n\n  # UI helpers\n  intl: ^0.19.0\n  cupertino_icons: ^1.0.8\n\ndev_dependencies:\n  flutter_test:\n    sdk: flutter\n  flutter_lints: ^4.0.0\n  build_runner: ^2.4.11\n  freezed: ^2.5.2\n  json_serializable: ^6.8.0\n  riverpod_generator: ^2.4.0\n  custom_lint: ^0.6.4\n  riverpod_lint: ^2.3.10\n\nflutter:\n  uses-material-design: true\n"
