        "readme": "# Task Manager – Spring Boot + Next.js + H2\n\nKompletní full-stack aplikace pro správu úkolů.\n\n## Technologie\n\n| Vrstva | Technologie |\n|---|---|\n| Backend | Spring Boot 3.3, Java 21 |\n| Databáze | H2 in-memory (bez instalace) |\n| ORM | Spring Data JPA + Hibernate |\n| Validace | Jakarta Validation |\n| Frontend | Next.js 14 (App Router), TypeScript |\n| Styling | Tailwind CSS |\n\n---\n\n## Struktura projektu\n\n```\ntaskmanager/\n├── backend/\n│   ├── pom.xml\n│   └── src/main/java/cz/taskmanager/\n│       ├── TaskmanagerApplication.java\n│       ├── model/          Task.java, Category.java, TaskStatus.java\n│       ├── repository/     TaskRepository.java, CategoryRepository.java\n│       ├── service/        TaskService.java\n│       ├── controller/     TaskController.java, CategoryController.java\n│       ├── dto/            TaskDto.java\n│       └── config/         CorsConfig.java, DataInitializer.java\n└── frontend/\n    ├── package.json\n    ├── next.config.js      (proxy /api -> localhost:8080)\n    ├── tailwind.config.js\n    └── src/\n        ├── types/          index.ts\n        ├── lib/            api.ts\n        ├── components/     TaskCard.tsx, TaskForm.tsx\n        └── app/\n            ├── layout.tsx\n            ├── page.tsx            (hlavní seznam)\n            ├── tasks/new/          (nový úkol)\n            ├── tasks/[id]/edit/    (editace)\n            └── categories/         (správa kategorií)\n```\n\n---\n\n## Spuštění\n\n### 1. Backend\n\n```bash\ncd backend\nmvn spring-boot:run\n```\n\nBackend běží na **http://localhost:8080**\n\nH2 konzole: **http://localhost:8080/h2-console**\n- JDBC URL: `jdbc:h2:mem:taskdb;DB_CLOSE_DELAY=-1;DB_CLOSE_ON_EXIT=FALSE`\n- Username: `sa`\n- Password: `admin`\n\n### 2. Frontend\n\n```bash\ncd frontend\nnpm install\nnpm run dev\n```\n\nFrontend běží na **http://localhost:3000**\n\n---\n\n## REST API\n\n### Úkoly\n\n| Metoda | Endpoint | Popis |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET | `/api/tasks` | Všechny úkoly |\n| GET | `/api/tasks?status=TODO` | Filtr podle stavu |\n| GET | `/api/tasks/{id}` | Detail úkolu |\n| POST | `/api/tasks` | Nový úkol |\n| PUT | `/api/tasks/{id}` | Aktualizace |\n| PATCH | `/api/tasks/{id}/status?status=DONE` | Změna stavu |\n| DELETE | `/api/tasks/{id}` | Smazání |\n\n### Kategorie\n\n| Metoda | Endpoint | Popis |\n|---|---|---|\n| GET | `/api/categories` | Všechny kategorie |\n| POST | `/api/categories` | Nová kategorie |\n| DELETE | `/api/categories/{id}` | Smazání |\n\n### Příklad POST /api/tasks\n\n```json\n{\n  \"title\": \"Nový úkol\",\n  \"description\": \"Popis úkolu\",\n  \"status\": \"TODO\",\n  \"categoryId\": 1\n}\n```\n\n### Stavy úkolu\n\n- `TODO` – k udělání\n- `IN_PROGRESS` – probíhá\n- `DONE` – hotovo\n\n---\n\n## Přechod na MySQL\n\nStačí změnit `application.properties`:\n\n```properties\nspring.datasource.url=jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/taskdb\nspring.datasource.username=root\nspring.datasource.password=heslo\nspring.datasource.driver-class-name=com.mysql.cj.jdbc.Driver\nspring.jpa.database-platform=org.hibernate.dialect.MySQLDialect\nspring.jpa.hibernate.ddl-auto=update\nspring.h2.console.enabled=false\n```\n\nA přidat dependency do `pom.xml`:\n\n```xml\n<dependency>\n  <groupId>com.mysql</groupId>\n  <artifactId>mysql-connector-j</artifactId>\n  <scope>runtime</scope>\n</dependency>\n```\n",
        "aboutTxt": null,
        "commentsTxt": null,
