        "readme": "# Todo App — Angular + Express + MySQL\n\nA full-stack todo application with category support.\n\n## Tech Stack\n- **Frontend**: Angular 17 (standalone components, TypeScript, SCSS)\n- **Backend**: Node.js + Express\n- **Database**: MySQL\n\n---\n\n## Project Structure\n\n```\ntodo-app/\n├── database/\n│   └── schema.sql          # MySQL schema + seed data\n├── backend/                # Express REST API\n│   ├── src/\n│   │   ├── config/db.js\n│   │   ├── controllers/\n│   │   │   ├── todos.controller.js\n│   │   │   └── categories.controller.js\n│   │   ├── routes/\n│   │   │   ├── todos.routes.js\n│   │   │   └── categories.routes.js\n│   │   └── index.js\n│   ├── .env.example\n│   └── package.json\n└── frontend/               # Angular app\n    ├── src/\n    │   ├── app/\n    │   │   ├── components/\n    │   │   │   ├── category-sidebar/\n    │   │   │   ├── todo-list/\n    │   │   │   ├── todo-item/\n    │   │   │   └── todo-form/\n    │   │   ├── models/todo.model.ts\n    │   │   ├── services/\n    │   │   │   ├── todo.service.ts\n    │   │   │   └── category.service.ts\n    │   │   ├── app.component.ts\n    │   │   └── app.config.ts\n    │   ├── environments/environment.ts\n    │   ├── styles.scss\n    │   └── index.html\n    ├── angular.json\n    └── package.json\n```\n\n---\n\n## Setup\n\n### 1. Database\n\n```bash\nmysql -u root -p < database/schema.sql\n```\n\n### 2. Backend\n\n```bash\ncd backend\ncp .env .env\n# Edit .env with your MySQL credentials\nnpm install\nnpm run dev       # starts on http://localhost:3000\n```\n\n### 3. Frontend\n\n```bash\ncd frontend\nnpm install\nnpm start         # starts on http://localhost:4200\n```\n\n---\n\n## API Endpoints\n\n### Todos\n| Method | Route | Description |\n|--------|-------|-------------|\n| GET    | /api/todos | Get all todos (supports ?category_id=&completed=) |\n| GET    | /api/todos/:id | Get single todo |\n| POST   | /api/todos | Create todo |\n| PUT    | /api/todos/:id | Update todo |\n| PATCH  | /api/todos/:id/toggle | Toggle complete |\n| DELETE | /api/todos/:id | Delete todo |\n\n### Categories\n| Method | Route | Description |\n|--------|-------|-------------|\n| GET    | /api/categories | Get all categories with todo count |\n| POST   | /api/categories | Create category |\n| PUT    | /api/categories/:id | Update category |\n| DELETE | /api/categories/:id | Delete category |\n\n---\n\n## Features\n- Create, edit, delete todos\n- Organise todos by categories with custom colours\n- Toggle todo completion\n- Filter todos by category\n- Pending / completed grouping\n\n---\n\n## Frontend Versions\n\nThere are two frontend implementations with identical Angular architecture but different UI approaches:\n\n| Aspect | `frontend` | `frontend-2` |\n|--------|-----------|--------------|\n| **UI Framework** | Custom SCSS only | Bootstrap 5 + Bootstrap Icons |\n| **Theme** | Dark (custom CSS variables, `#6366f1` accent) | Light (Bootstrap defaults) |\n| **Styling** | Component-scoped SCSS files | Bootstrap utility classes in templates |\n| **Icon Library** | None | Bootstrap Icons |\n| **Linting** | ESLint configured | Removed |\n| **Build output** | `dist/todo-app-frontend` | `dist/todo-app-frontend-2` |\n\nBoth versions share the same component tree, services, models, and API integration. Only the presentation layer differs.\n\nTo run `frontend-2`:\n\n```bash\ncd frontend-2\nnpm install\nnpm start         # starts on http://localhost:4200\n```\n",
        "aboutTxt": "The two folders are functionally identical─but─differ─mainly─in─UI framework and styling approach:───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n\r\n  ┌──────────────┬─────────────────────────────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────┐──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\r\n  │    Aspect    │                  frontend                   │               frontend-2               │\r\n  ├──────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ UI Framework │ Custom SCSS only                            │ Bootstrap 5 + Bootstrap Icons          │\r\n  ├──────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ Theme        │ Dark (custom CSS variables, #6366f1 accent) │ Light (Bootstrap defaults)             │\r\n  ├──────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ Styling      │ Component-scoped SCSS files                 │ Bootstrap utility classes in templates │\r\n  ├──────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ Linting      │ ESLint configured                           │ Removed                                │\r\n  ├──────────────┼─────────────────────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────┤\r\n  │ Build        │ Simpler output                              │ Bundles Bootstrap CSS/JS               │\r\n  └──────────────┴─────────────────────────────────────────────┴────────────────────────────────────────┘\r\n\r\n  In short: frontend is a custom dark-themed app; frontend-2 is a refactored version using Bootstrap 5 with a light theme. The Angular architecture, components, services, and API calls are the same in both.\r\n",
        "commentsTxt": null,
